266
00:33:06,350 --> 00:33:09,160
Gil Dong!

267
00:33:10,610 --> 00:33:12,070
Generál Hong!

268
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:22,900
Gil Dong!

269
00:33:22,900 --> 00:33:24,200
To je ono!

270
00:33:38,730 --> 00:33:41,780
Generál Hong!
Vzchop sa!

271
