boli uväznení suguidanmi?

287
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,640
Áno, pane!

288
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:11,720
Nechajte ich,
nech sa o Honga postarajú!

289
00:35:13,130 --> 00:35:17,760
