342
00:42:15,700 --> 00:42:16,730
Si v poriadku?

343
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:22,630
Utekajte!
Vráťte sa!

344
00:42:22,630 --> 00:42:24,510
Rýchlo!

345
00:42:26,940 --> 00:42:31,170
Prineste mi Hong Gil Dongovu hlavu!

346
00:43:06,680 --> 00:43:08,980
