350
00:44:20,320 --> 00:44:23,030
Útok!

351
00:44:23,030 --> 00:44:24,930
Poďme!

352
00:44:41,780 --> 00:44:43,790
Už je všetko v poriadku.

353
00:44:43,790 --> 00:44:47,250
